conference.content:
Join us for 3 full days of Insights, Inspiration " Community around PHP and Web Technology! June 25, 26 and 27 2020 - RAI Amsterdam
Learn new stuff and get inspired by 50+ speakers " 500+ fellow attendees: join our Tutorial Day Thursday June 25 with master classes from the PHP " Web Tech community. Followed by the main Conference Days Friday and Saturday June 26 and 27, 2 days full of talks and social activities.
